# - App will use static fallbacks (quiz data, Socratic questions)
# - All core features remain functional
# 
# FOR HYBRID DEPLOYMENT (Optional Backend):
# - Set URLs to your production backends
# - Features gracefully degrade if backends unavailable
# - Best for public sites with optional enhanced features
#
